---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import styles from './PrivacyPage.module.css';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../shared/site';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Bill Bergquist"
  description="Privacy policy for billbergquist.dev. How your data is collected, used, and protected."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <div class={styles.page}>
    <header class={styles.header}>
      <h1 class={styles.title}>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class={styles.updated}>Last updated: March 9, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class={styles.content}>
      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>What This Site Collects</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand how visitors find and use the
          site. Cloudflare Analytics is privacy-first: it doesn't use cookies, doesn't track
          individual users, and doesn't collect personal information. It measures things like page
          views, referrers, and device types in aggregate. No data is sold to advertisers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Contact Form</h2>
        <p>
          If you fill out the contact form on the services page, your name, email, and message
          are sent to me through Netlify Forms. I use this information only to respond to your
          inquiry. I don't add you to any mailing list or share your information with anyone.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This site does not use cookies for analytics. Cloudflare Web Analytics is cookieless.
          Clerk, which handles authentication for RetroRetro and Craps, may set its own cookies
          as needed to manage your login session.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Authentication (Clerk)</h2>
        <p>
          The arcade section of this site uses <a href="https://clerk.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class={styles.link}>Clerk</a> for
          user authentication. If you create an account for RetroRetro or Craps, Clerk
          stores your login credentials and session data. You can review Clerk's privacy policy
          on their website. I don't have access to your password or authentication tokens.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Your Data Is Not Sold</h2>
        <p>
          I don't sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties. Period.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class={styles.sectionTitle}>Questions</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can reach me at{' '}
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class={styles.link}>
            {CONTACT_EMAIL}
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
